{"tid":2055399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高雄市議長墮斃  綠營議員涉發表不敬言論  遭圍攻","createTime":"2020-06-08T02:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T02:58:33.000Z","uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a68133a40a3d69e74153e94a1af7e10432e5bf2b","tid":2055399,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200608/W2FS3MQYGZQE4E24MBN2KFG6WQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200608%2FW2FS3MQYGZQE4E24MBN2KFG6WQ%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3Kaof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=6fdae31f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200608%2FW2FS3MQYGZQE4E24MBN2KFG6WQ%2F&h=e26099d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200608/W2FS3MQYGZQE4E24MBN2KFG6WQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n高雄市議長墮斃 震撼台政壇 <br />\n涉發表不敬言論 綠營議員遭圍攻<br />\n<br />\n高雄市議長許崑源在市長韓國瑜罷免案通過當晚，從家中墮樓身亡，震撼台灣政壇。國民黨前主席吳敦義昨晨前往墮樓處弔唁，與妻子獻花並三鞠躬致哀，受訪時泣不成聲，哽咽直言：「昨天（周六）知道這個噩耗，實在是非常令人痛心。」事件還引發社會撕裂，民進黨籍桃園市議員王浩宇前晚在社交網站發表被指對死者不敬的留言，引來「韓粉」不滿揚言要包圍其辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n(節錄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-rW12ERxCuH52yHOGodgELMPt4Q=/802x544/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRKBZJO7RKYHXNXKNJZNFPWEOU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-rW12ERxCuH52yHOGodgELMPt4Q%3D%2F802x544%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRKBZJO7RKYHXNXKNJZNFPWEOU.gif&h=c23ee69a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許崑源在facebook留下這句後墮樓亡。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民進黨籍桃園市議員王浩宇前晚得悉許崑源墮樓身亡後，卻在facebook留言稱：「嚇死人，是賭很大嗎？」同黨的台北市議員梁文傑也在網上留言：「力挺韓國瑜！高雄市議長許崑源晚間墜樓身亡。」兩人發帖不久後遭網民責難後匆匆刪文。韓粉「杏仁哥」因為不滿王浩宇，呼籲網民今天到王桃園中壢的辦公室集結。王表示因為「韓粉」集會可能丟水球和雞蛋，為了避免造成衝突，決定服務處暫停服務一天。<br />\n<br />\n對於兩名民進黨民意代表網上言論被指「消費」，國民黨主席江啟臣昨到殯儀館致意時稱，希望悲劇到此為止，又指台灣社會不是只有政治，現在最重要的是安撫家屬，譴責政治人物這時在傷口灑鹽。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-06-06/900/20200606004393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-06-06%2F900%2F20200606004393.jpg&h=85d05dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"277c7ae945f7833817077ccd71188bb0cccfbfa2","tid":2055399,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"痴線 講事實都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}